---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>About | Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen font-sans">
    <header class="bg-green-900 text-white py-6 shadow">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</h1>
        <nav class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <a href="/" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="mr-6 hover:underline">About</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="hover:underline">Blog</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10 max-w-2xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6 mb-6">
        <img src="/images/Me.png" alt="Christen Thompson" class="rounded-lg w-48 h-48 object-cover shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">About Christen Thompson</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">Hi, I'm Christen Thompson, and I'm running for Heber City Council. I am passionate about preserving the unique character of Heber Valley while ensuring a bright future for all residents. My campaign is built on the preserving open space, clean water, clean air, affordability, and creating better trails and paths.
          
          
          </p>

          <p>
          I have extensive experience working as a software engineer and leader across teams envisioning, designing and delivering products. This has required me to learn how to effectively communicate, prioritize and get things done.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2">My Vision</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
        <li>Protecting our open spaces</li>
        <li>Ensuring clean water and air for future generations</li>
        <li>Promoting affordable living and smart growth</li>
        <li>Expanding trails and paths for a connected, healthy community</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6 text-gray-700">Thank you for your support. Together, we can keep Heber a wonderful place to live, work, and play!</p>
    </main>
    <footer class="bg-green-900 text-white py-4 mt-10 text-center">
      &copy; 2025 Christen Thompson for Heber City Council
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
